<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Regulation lims:pit-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:current-date="2025-07-24" lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024902" lims:id="1024902" regulation-type="SOR" xml:lang="en" xmlns:lims="http://justice.gc.ca/lims"><Identification lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024903" lims:id="1024903"><InstrumentNumber>SOR/98-50</InstrumentNumber><RegistrationDate><Date><YYYY>1997</YYYY><MM>12</MM><DD>29</DD></Date></RegistrationDate><ConsolidationDate lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22"><Date><YYYY>2025</YYYY><MM>7</MM><DD>25</DD></Date></ConsolidationDate><EnablingAuthority lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024905" lims:id="1024905"><XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="C-52.6">CUSTOMS ACT</XRefExternal></EnablingAuthority><LongTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024906" lims:id="1024906">Diversion of Imported Goods Exemption Regulations</LongTitle><RegulationMakerOrder><RegulationMaker>P.C.</RegulationMaker><OrderNumber>1997-2022</OrderNumber><Date><YYYY>1997</YYYY><MM>12</MM><DD>29</DD></Date></RegulationMakerOrder></Identification><Order lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024907" lims:id="1024907"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024908" lims:id="1024908" language-align="yes" format-ref="indent-0-0" list-item="no"><Text>His Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of National Revenue, pursuant to subsection 32.2(7)<FootnoteRef idref="footnotea_e">a</FootnoteRef>of the <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="C-52.6">Customs Act</XRefExternal><FootnoteRef idref="footnoteb_e">b</FootnoteRef>, hereby makes the annexed <XRefExternal reference-type="regulation" link="SOR-98-50">Diversion of Imported Goods Exemption Regulations</XRefExternal>.</Text><Footnote id="footnotea_e" placement="section" status="official"><Label>a</Label><Text>S.C. 1997, c. 36, s. 152</Text></Footnote><Footnote id="footnoteb_e" placement="section" status="official"><Label>b</Label><Text>R.S., c. 1 (2nd Supp.)</Text></Footnote></Provision></Order><Body lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024909" lims:id="1024909"><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024910" lims:id="1024910" level="1"><TitleText>Interpretation</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024911" lims:id="1024911"><Label>1</Label><Text>The definitions in this section apply in these Regulations.</Text><Definition lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024912" lims:id="1024912" generate-in-text="no"><Text><DefinedTermEn>Act</DefinedTermEn> means the <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="C-52.6">Customs Act</XRefExternal>. (<DefinedTermFr>Loi</DefinedTermFr>)</Text></Definition><Definition lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024913" lims:id="1024913" generate-in-text="no"><Text><DefinedTermEn>emergency</DefinedTermEn> means a medical emergency, fire, flood or any disaster that threatens life, property or the environment. (<DefinedTermFr>urgence</DefinedTermFr>)</Text></Definition></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024914" lims:id="1024914" level="1"><TitleText>Exemption for Emergency Use</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024915" lims:id="1024915"><Label>2</Label><Text>Imported goods that, in response to an emergency, are temporarily diverted to a use other than that for which they were released are exempt from the operation of subsection 32.2(6) of the Act for the period during which the goods are used in response to the emergency.</Text></Section><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024916" lims:id="1024916"><Label>3</Label><Text>Imported goods that are consumed in response to an emergency are exempt from the operation of subsection 32.2(6) of the Act.</Text></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024917" lims:id="1024917" level="1"><TitleText>Repeal</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024918" lims:id="1024918"><Label>4</Label><Text>[Repeal]</Text></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024919" lims:id="1024919" level="1"><TitleText>Coming into Force</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1024920" lims:id="1024920" type="transitional"><Label>5</Label><Text>These Regulations come into force on January 1, 1998.</Text></Section></Body></Regulation>